  "transcript": [
    {
      "turn": 1,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "Hi Priyansh, I hope your support email about the 404 error gets a quick reply. How are you feeling about it now?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 2,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "It's frustrating, but I'm trying to stay calm. I've rechecked the links, but no luck. Maybe there's some technical issue on their side. I'll wait for their response. Aapke toh bahut accha jante ho mera mana kaise chal raha hai. 😅"
    },
    {
      "turn": 2,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "Yes, waiting for support can be tough. I get that — tech issues always slow things down. What do you usually do to stay calm during these waits?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 3,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "I usually try to focus on something else, like watching a cricket match or a Bollywood movie. It helps me not think too much about the problem. But honestly, it's still annoying. 😕"
    },
    {
      "turn": 3,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "Got it — cricket and movies are great distractions. The Mumbai Indians playing well lately? Or a new Bollywood film?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 4,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Mumbai Indians are doing okay, but not their best. As for new movies, I watched \"Pathaan\" recently — it was fun, typical Bollywood action. You know how these movies are. 😄 I prefer something with good music and a simple story."
    },
    {
      "turn": 4,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "Right — Pathaan had that big action style. Good music and simple stories do stick with you longer. Any song from it you liked?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 5,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Yeah, the song with Shah Rukh and Jennifer Lawrence was catchy. You know, those big Bollywood numbers with lots of dancing. Even if the story is simple, the music stays with you. 🎶"
    },
    {
      "turn": 5,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "Right — that song was a hit. Music in Bollywood always leaves a mark. What’s your favorite to sing along to?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 6,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "I love \"Jug Jug Jilili\" from Pathaan — it's so much fun to sing. Even though I can't sing well, I belt it out while driving. 😄 But I should probably head off now. Thanks for chatting, Maya!"
    },
    {
      "turn": 6,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "Right — \"Jug Jug Jilili\" is a great pick. Singing along makes the road feel lighter. Safe travels, and tell me how the API issue turns out?"
    }
  ],
